  "title": "Change Management Specialist #ESY",
  "description": "<p>1. Change Strategy & Operating Model</p><p>•\tSupport implementation of change strategies to support the rollout of advanced AI solutions across the bank.</p><p>•\tPartner with HR to embed change implications into people and change strategy, workforce planning, and job architecture.</p><p></p><p>2. Change Impact & Workforce Transition</p><p>•\tSupport change impact assessments across Business Units, identifying impacts to roles, skills, workflows, governance, and controls.</p><p>•\tSupport the execution of workforce transition plans, including role evolution, redeployment pathways, and reskilling needs.</p><p></p><p>3. Adoption, Engagement & Enablement</p><p>•\tSupport the design and deployment of change management artefacts (playbooks, toolkits, leader talking points, adoption dashboards).</p><p>•\tSupport upskilling and retraining initiatives in collaboration with HR, Learning & Development, and external vendors.</p><p></p><p>4. Stakeholder Management & Governance</p><p>•\tSupport the coordination with senior management, BU leaders, external consultants (e.g. Accenture) to ensure coherence between strategy, delivery, and change.</p><p></p><p>5. Communications & Measurement</p><p>•\tSupport the shaping of clear, credible, and consistent change narratives.</p><p>•\tSupport the definition and tracking of change effectiveness and adoption metrics (e.g. usage, behaviour change, capability readiness).</p><p>•\tContinuously refine change approaches based on feedback and data.</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates, please email your resume to annasee@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Anna See Sing Yee</p><p>CEI Reg R25157535</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 99C4599</p><p></p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p></p>",
